{"tid":152943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全城趕買樓？】3大新盤兩日勁收4600票","createTime":"2017-03-12T08:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T11:27:57.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf9a14217214addd53ac3a2f05ef21b265a1bcc","tid":152943,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170311/photo/bkn-20170311203835922-0311_00842_001_01b.jpg?20170312065422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170311%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170311203835922-0311_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20170312065422&h=80b9e837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20170312/photo/0312-00202-001h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170312%2Fphoto%2F0312-00202-001h1.jpg&h=09592e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170310/photo/bkn-20170310210936118-0310_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170310212945\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170310%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170310210936118-0310_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20170310212945&h=7838fa6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓市進入亢奮狀態，三大新盤適時推出鬥搶客，睇樓客逼爆售樓處；而繼周五三盤同步收票共收逾1500票後，今日收票情況更再進一步上衝，綜合發展公布及市場消息，三盤兩日勁收約4,600票。<br />\n<br />\n其中新鴻基地產(00016)西南九龍匯璽，市場消息指，截至晚上兩日累收約2,000票，入票情況熱烈。至於會德豐地產將軍澳南MONTEREY，今日入票登記達1,300張，兩日收票料超過1,800張。<br />\n<br />\n另長實地產(01113)旗下馬鞍山星漣海，市傳兩日收票近800張，發展商有見及此，加推2號價單49伙應市，價單折實平均呎價14,589港元，加價1%至2%。<br />\n<br />\n新地匯璽備受市場注目，記者現場所見，準買家於售樓處樓下的電梯大堂大排長龍，連續兩日有多達數百人「打蛇餅等睇樓」的墟冚場面。市場消息，樓盤今日錄逾1,000票，兩日合共錄約2,000票。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">據悉，匯璽首張價單共210伙，價單平均呎價24,357港元，折實平均呎價18,998元。最平單位為1B座10樓D室開放式單位，折實售價逾491.71萬元。</span><br />\n<br />\n另將軍澳南MONTEREY，會德豐地產常務董事黃光耀指，項目昨開始收票，截至晚上八點，兩日收票數量逾1,800張，較首張價單186伙超額逾8倍；他更指未來加推單位一定會加價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170311/bkn-20170311203835922-0311_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170311%2Fbkn-20170311203835922-0311_00842_001.html&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f66cede0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170311/bkn-20170311203835922-0311_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6fecb0b80aae357cb8f5d06e35fb159370a3b969","tid":152943,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"1997，2007，2017 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b5117efe84c7d5724afc06f7263713d0702639","tid":152943,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0ee50aea1efba14edc29c600fcdd825f5686878","tid":152943,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1997，2007，2017 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd63027d14cb9317c6e5af4658bff9c1bee236d1","tid":152943,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"加息期先買樓，港豬真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70abe4ea9412cb09fe73055c14f65ce3d01532db","tid":152943,"uid":51215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"買多啲快啲谷爆個市"},{"pid":"54c74376d5d943423cfa10ad5ed2c6d81ddbac24","tid":152943,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加息期先買樓，港豬真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse